#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:7
msgid "Active Directory/LDAP integration offers the following benefits:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:9
msgid ""
"Single sign-on. Users can sign-in to Mattermost with their AD/LDAP "
"credentials."
msgstr ""

