#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:76
msgid "If \"AD/LDAP Test\" button fails, how can I troubleshoot the connection?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:78
msgid ""
"Check that your AD/LDAP connection settings are correct by running an "
"AD/LDAP user query in an external system. See LDAP Connection Test "
"Example."
