#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:166
msgid "I see the log error LDAP Result Code 4 \"Size Limit Exceeded\""
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:168
msgid ""
"This indicates your AD/LDAP server configuration has a maximum page size "
"set and the query coming from Mattermost is returning a result set in "
"excess of that limit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:170
msgid ""
"To address this issue you can set the max page size in your Mattermost "
"configuration to match the limit on your AD/LDAP server. This will return"
" a sequence of result sets that do not exceed the max page size, rather "
"than returning all results in a single query."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment/sso-ldap.md:172
msgid ""
"If the error is still occurring, it is likely that no AD/LDAP users have "
"logged into Mattermost yet. Ensure that at least 1 AD/LDAP user has "
"logged into Mattermost and re-run the sync. The error should disappear at"
" that point."
